OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779719233
OL,3,CPrince William heads to Isles of
OL,4,CScilly during his tour of the West
OL,5,CCountry
OL,7,FPrince William will visit the Isles of
OL,8,FScilly today, Friday 22 May, as he
OL,9,Fcontinues his tour of the West Country.
OL,11,FThe future king spent Thursday 21 May,
OL,12,Fvisiting new Duchy of Cornwall homes
OL,13,Fin Nansledan, Newquay.
OL,15,FToday, the Duke of Cornwall will
OL,16,Ftravel to St Mary's, where he'll head
OL,17,Fto the Isles of Scilly Hospital to
OL,18,Fmeet staff, patients and open a new
OL,19,Ffacility which has increased medical
OL,20,Fcapacity to the Isles.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
