OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779719233
OL,3,CPrince William heads to Isles of
OL,4,CScilly during his tour of the West
OL,5,CCountry
OL,7,FThe Duke will then see the near
OL,8,Fcomplete construction site of ten new
OL,9,Fsustainable homes being delivered by
OL,10,Fthe Duchy of Cornwall.
OL,12,FThe development has been designed to
OL,13,Fhelp tackle the Isles' acute housing
OL,14,Fshortage, with homes prioritised for
OL,15,Fthose who have lived on the Isles of
OL,16,FScilly for more than five years, or
OL,17,Fwho currently work on the islands.
OL,19,FOnce complete, the homes will feature
OL,20,Fhigh levels of insulation, positive
OL,21,Fventilation throughout and rooftop
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779719233
OL,3,CPrince William heads to Isles of
OL,4,CScilly during his tour of the West
OL,5,CCountry
OL,7,Fsolar panels. Each property will also
OL,8,Finclude a dedicated parking space for
OL,9,Fthe island car-share scheme, with
OL,10,Fprovision for electric vehicle
OL,11,Fcharging points.
OL,13,FThe homes are expected to welcome
OL,14,Ftheir first residents in winter 2026.
OL,16,FAfter visiting the new development,
OL,17,Fthe Duke will meet local emergency
OL,18,Fresponders to hear about the role they
OL,19,Fplayed when the islands were battered
OL,20,Fby Storm Goretti earlier this year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
