OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779719233
OL,3,CPrince William heads to Isles of
OL,4,CScilly during his tour of the West
OL,5,CCountry
OL,7,FThe Isles of Scilly experienced
OL,8,Fsignificant loss to its shelterbelt
OL,9,Ftrees during the January storm, which
OL,10,Fplay a vital role in protecting
OL,11,Fcommunities from high winds and storms.
OL,13,FDuring the visit, The Duke will
OL,14,Freplant a shelterbelt tree and reflect
OL,15,Fon the Duchy's role in providing
OL,16,Fadditional resources, organising
OL,17,Fessential repairs and commissioning
OL,18,Fexpert assessments from surveyors and
OL,19,Fforestry
OL,21,Fspecialists.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
